üîç What is happening here?

await wppconnect.create()	            Creates a session and returns the client instance
catchLinkCode	                        Called when WhatsApp sends a login code to the phone
start(client)	                          Your function where you begin sending messages, getting groups, contacts, etc.



‚ö† Why it took long

WPPConnect tries to download Chromium (same as Puppeteer).
This file is 100MB+ so on slow network it takes time.

If you want to skip this (for development on Windows), run:

set PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD=true
npm i @wppconnect-team/wppconnect